### Dashboard API Documentation

#### Get Readiness Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/readiness
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

#### Get Adoption Dashboard  
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/adoption
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

#### Get Watchlist Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

#### Dashboard with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/readiness?department=technology&dateRange=30
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

